    "body": "It looks like we can save 7 gas per addition:\r\n```\r\nlet z := add(x, y)\r\nif gt(x, not(y)) { revert(0, 0) }\r\n```\r\nwrt\r\n```\r\nlet z := add(x, y)\r\nif lt(z, x) { revert(0, 0) }\r\n```",
